item.title: 12-30-18Sunday Morning Coffee
item.description: A quick review of Netfix’s Bird Box, my opinion on the stupid argument of the “Legends of Podcasting” bad mouthing Anchor. How They have based to their argument from a false perspective and the future of TruckinNutz and my other podcast Driving Common Sense.
